data.description: This amazing home in Southeast Winter Haven is basically new! New Roof, New HVAC, New Water Heater, New Pool screened enclosure, New Pool Pump, New Flooring, New cabinets, New Paint, new pool solar, new granite, the guest shower has just been redone and tub was removed for a beautiful walk in shower, the pool just had new marcite sprayed and the deck a new coat of paint, new countertops throughout the home, showers were refaced. The list can go on and on. This four bedroom three bath pool home is ready for you, located near everything you would ever need.
